{"tid":1857504,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[透明公開]民間集會團隊2020年一月綜合財政報告","createTime":"2020-02-02T08:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T08:43:49.000Z","uid":42194,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea7031a54eca0c9dedfaeba769b1d6bdd315b88","tid":1857504,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"民間集會團隊2020年1月綜合財政報告<br />\n<br />\n抗爭踏入第七個月，香港人仍然憑著堅毅，勇敢去走上街頭，繼續抗爭。民間集會團隊(民集)也繼續與香港人一起齊上齊落，在一月主辦了兩次大型活動，及一次贊助活動。<br />\n<br />\n現附上民集2020年1月的綜合財政報告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WT8zsBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT8zsBM.jpg&h=8f6100c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JVh9P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JVh9P6.jpg&h=fc51b215&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzqxYJs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzqxYJs.jpg&h=f1ba5e61&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n縱使我們與香港人在剛過去的一月受盡不同程度的打壓，如遊行被無理反對，民集發言人被無理拘捕，最近大家更一同面對疫症威脅，防疫物資短缺，然而抗爭並不會就此結束。民集全力支持醫護界罷工抗爭，亦請各位手足發揮創意和毅力，一起堅持下去，好好保重，直到我們在煲底下相聚之時。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\n2020年2月2日<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n參與/洽詢合作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCATeam_bot&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9N%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=1a0aae17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n我們的最新動向/合作洽詢：<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9N%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=1c85c67a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT%2F&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9N%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=cecce175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/</a><br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9N%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=7faba12e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\nTelegram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/CivilAssemblyTeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilAssemblyTeam&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9N%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=fcf6bc67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilAssemblyTeam</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然民集宣佈左因為疫情暫停舉辦需要不反嘅公眾活動一個月，但我地積極考慮緊試下各種不同嘅方式，各位手足有idea  嘅不妨俾D意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d7188152203658ae73c234a2146061994924da","tid":1857504,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"447119b5e07f60801af399f7891b7677910ba1cc","tid":1857504,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:19:50.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"3d5203c07f1a9ef85eaba1dc3cf11f2c728af732","tid":1857504,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"c386ee7de35de81bbe31a1e881f99227b6b87fb4","tid":1857504,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"f0361a11a49835b06e5427ba524005be84aec2fa","tid":1857504,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:20:20.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"883fa5d0728a0d897d66a6939608776bf601267